title: Yosemite National Park: Photo Gallery
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia     Photo Gallery              Photo Gallery                    Historical Images   39 Photos  A sampling of historical images from the park's collection. For further information, or to obtain a photographic or digital copy of the original photograph, contact Yosemite Research Library, National Park Service, PO Box 577, Yosemite, CA 95389; phone 209/372-0280. In each photo description, you'll find a specific number that you will need to reference when requesting a photo.          Hetch Hetchy Wildflowers   38 Photos  A sampling of flowers blooming along the 2.5-mile trail to Wapama Falls in early June 2013.
